<title>
Transaxle Left Case Disassembly and Reassembly
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENBP70A5206010">Manual Transaxle Unit Dismounting and Remounting</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENBP70A5206014">Manual Transaxle Assembly Components</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A5206017001">
<title>
Disassembly
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove oil gutter (1), if necessary.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I5RW0B520036.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "53.253mm" ver = "01" gw = "186" gh = "134"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove oil seal using flat-bladed screwdriver or the like.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove differential side bearing outer race (1) and shim using special tools.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B015">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09942-15511">
09942–15511
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B016">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09944-96011">
09944–96011
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I5RW0B520037.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "54.157mm" ver = "01" gw = "182" gh = "137"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove countershaft left bearing outer race (1) and shim using special tools.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B017">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09942-15511">
09942–15511
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L5B018">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09944-96011">
09944–96011
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAY301520033.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "56.247mm" ver = "02" gw = "184" gh = "143"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<c-change/>
<servinfosub id = "AENBP70A5206017002">
<title>
Reassembly
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install oil gutter (1), if removed.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I5RW0B520036.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "53.253mm" ver = "01" gw = "186" gh = "134"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Select countershaft left side bearing shim and differential left side bearing shim as follows.
</ptxt>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Keep pressing outer race with 35 N (3.67 kgf, 7.87 lbf) and turn countershaft assembly and differential case 10 times or more.
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Measure distance “a” of countershaft assembly (1) and “e” of differential assembly (2).
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Measure depth “b” and “g” of transaxle left case (3) and “c” and “f” of transaxle right case (4).
</ptxt>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Calculate the clearance of “d” and “h” by the following formulas.
</ptxt>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "1" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "3.444in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Clearance of “d” = Depth “b” + Depth “c” – Distance “a”
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "1" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "3.444in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1">
<ptxt>
Clearance of “h” = Depth “f” + Depth “g” – Distance “e”
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAY301520065.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "110.147mm" ver = "01" gw = "210" gh = "296"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
